Didier and my son, he's Talma's hubby...and he is also great with kids, he is like a kiddies magnet!!! lol! My sweetie, Fred!Enjoying the compagny of our friends! I wish everyone a good weekend!See ya next time!

Today , I did nothing special, I went to the hospital to do my excersises for my backproblems, it went well,but now my back hurts a little , but tomorrow it will be fine! I hope, Fred and I gonna go searching for a tvkabinet, now our Cd's and Dvd's are exposed to our kids and Till the youngest one likes to grab them and I don't like him to play with my dvdcollection!So it's important we find a kabinet that has a closed section as well and is big enough to store them too!

Hildekittenn is gonna make some neath hairclips for my daughter Helena, I can't hardly wait , because they are so cute especially I like the pussycats , so cute!
